[captain_hilda]: The town's leadership has been focused on preparing for the coming winter and the goblin raids, but... whispers in the tavern hint at tensions beneath the surface. Some are wary of our new recruitments, suspecting outside influences. I must admit, your concerns are not unfounded. Have you heard anything that might shed light on these rumors?